      "Tidal heating from Jupiter melts much of Io's interior.",
      "Some of its mountains stand taller than Mount Everest.",
      "Io feeds a giant torus of charged particles around Jupiter.",
      "Voyager 1 discovered active volcanism on Io in 1979.",
      "Radiation near Io would be quickly fatal to an unshielded human."
