      "Its odd 'cantaloupe terrain' is found nowhere else known.",
      "It is similar in size and makeup to the dwarf planet Pluto.",
      "Voyager 2 is the only spacecraft to have visited it, in 1989.",
      "It is slowly spiraling inward and will eventually break apart."
