      "Its reddish polar cap may be colored by methane stolen from Pluto.",
      "Its canyon system is in places deeper than Earth's Grand Canyon.",
      "New Horizons revealed its surface in detail during a 2015 flyby.",
      "It is about half the diameter of Pluto itself."
